reviewText: Love Louise Dreyfus? She's funny as always, but what a potty mouth!
great show loving every minute of it

My main negative comment relates to language.  I am not a prude, and I know tha the f--- word is often used by younger people today, but the frequency of its use in this series is ridiculous, and in my opinion detracts from content and humor.
Arrived on time and was exactly what I was expecting.
